<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard - Clean To Do List</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen font-sans p-4 md:p-8">

    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        
        <header class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center mb-10 gap-4">
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">My Workspace</h1>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">Kelola dan selesaikan prioritasmu hari ini.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
                <button class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl text-gray-700 text-sm font-medium transition-colors shadow-sm">
                    Filter Tugas
                </button>
                <button class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-white hover:bg-red-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl text-red-600 text-sm font-medium transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 shadow-sm">
                    <span>Logout</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </header>

        <form action="#" class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-3 mb-10 bg-white p-2.5 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
            <input type="text" 
                class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 bg-transparent text-gray-800 placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none text-base" 
                placeholder="Apa yang ingin kamu kerjakan hari ini?" required>
            <button type="submit" 
                class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-xl shadow-sm shadow-blue-600/30 transition-colors">
                Tambah Task
            </button>
        </form>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 items-stretch">
            
            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-400 rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-200 group flex flex-col justify-between h-full shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
                <div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                        <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 text-xs font-semibold rounded-md border border-blue-100">#101</span>
                        <button class="text-gray-400 hover:text-red-500 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 7l-.867 12.142A2 2 0 0116.138 21H7.862a2 2 0 01-1.995-1.858L5 7m5 4v6m4-6v6m1-10V4a1 1 0 00-1-1h-4a1 1 0 00-1 1v3M4 7h16"></path></svg>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-800 font-medium text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">Membangun struktur routing Express.js menggunakan pola arsitektur modular yang rapi seperti index.js dan direktori api/.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-4 border-t border-gray-100 mt-auto">
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-medium">26 Mei 2026</p>
                    <button class="w-6 h-6 rounded border-2 border-gray-300 flex items-center justify-center hover:border-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors"></button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-200 group flex flex-col justify-between h-full">
                <div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                        <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-gray-200 text-gray-500 text-xs font-semibold rounded-md border border-gray-200">#102</span>
                        <button class="text-gray-400 hover:text-red-500 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 7l-.867 12.142A2 2 0 0116.138 21H7.862a2 2 0 01-1.995-1.858L5 7m5 4v6m4-6v6m1-10V4a1 1 0 00-1-1h-4a1 1 0 00-1 1v3M4 7h16"></path></svg>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-lg leading-relaxed line-through mb-4">Desain UI halaman Login dengan warna dasar putih dan aksen biru.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-4 border-t border-gray-200 mt-auto">
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-medium">25 Mei 2026</p>
                    <button class="w-6 h-6 rounded bg-blue-600 border-2 border-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-400 rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-200 group flex flex-col justify-between h-full shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
                <div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                        <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 text-xs font-semibold rounded-md border border-blue-100">#103</span>
                        <button class="text-gray-400 hover:text-red-500 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 7l-.867 12.142A2 2 0 0116.138 21H7.862a2 2 0 01-1.995-1.858L5 7m5 4v6m4-6v6m1-10V4a1 1 0 00-1-1h-4a1 1 0 00-1 1v3M4 7h16"></path></svg>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-800 font-medium text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">Menyiapkan koneksi database MySQL dan membuat tabel 'tasks' dengan kolom is_completed.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-4 border-t border-gray-100 mt-auto">
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-medium">26 Mei 2026</p>
                    <button class="w-6 h-6 rounded border-2 border-gray-300 flex items-center justify-center hover:border-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors"></button>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>